        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Restraining Russian Imperialism Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the President to impose all available Russia-related sanctions against each individual and entity that meet the criteria for such sanctions until the Russian government removes all of its armed forces from the Donbas region of Ukraine. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
